: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(107, 107, 107); font-family: ''Open Sans'', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23.8px;">\r\n	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">(e)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>What is the function of safety valve?</p>\r\n', 'a270e-different-kinds-of-boilers.jpg', 'Published', 0, 0, '2016-03-01 08:55:05', 0);
